  required initial-spin averaging version: initial_spin_average_v2
  unpolarized decomposition: 1/4 average over electron and proton helicities
  single-electron-polarization decomposition: 1/2 average over proton helicity
  longitudinal decomposition uses signed electron-helicity response components
