  targets: C_{ep}, C_{p\gamma}, C_{e\gamma}
  max spin cases per target: 2
  top rows per target/spin case: 80
  cluster radius: 0.42
  max clusters per target/spin case: 4
  no PDF combines different E_gamma values or polarization configs
